(26, 3, 'Ah Dead Space. My favorite horror game and just all around amazing game. Anytime someone asks me for a new spooky game or if they should try Dead Space my answer is always yes! Great horror and scares without using the same ol bag of tricks too often. Punchy and satisfying gameplay. And some of the best art design and atmosphere in a game of all time. I highly recommend this game!\r\n\r\nAlso keep in mind. the PC port is a bit rough out of the box, but the good news is the issues are pretty easily fixable! and don\'t require much effort to fix at all. just take a look at the steam guides or even google the fixes, easy.', 4),
(26, 5, 'Twelve years after it\'s release, Dead Space remains as a glorious achivement, a beautiful storm of time and place that resulted in one of the best action-horror games ever made.\r\n\r\nAn absolute panic-inducing gorefest, scaled perfectly from start to finish, with it\'s deliciously enjoyable arsenal and an atmosphere built on artistic technical prowess that aged like a wine keeping it just as good for years to come.\r\n\r\nOustanding gem of a title that stood the test of time.', 5),
(26, 7, ' ⣿⣿⣿⣿⠘⡿⢛⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣧⢻⣿⣿⠃⠸⣿⣿⣿          \r\n   ⣿⣿⣿⣿⢀⠼⣛⣛⣭⢭⣟⣛⣛⣛⠿⠿⢆⡠⢿⣿⣿          \r\n   ⠸⣿⣿⢣⢶⣟⣿⣖⣿⣷⣻⣮⡿⣽⣿⣻⣖⣶⣤⣭⡉          \r\n     ⢹⠣⣛⣣⣭⣭⣭⣁⡛⠻⢽⣿⣿⣿⣿⢻⣿⣿⣿⣽⡧⡄      \r\n       ⣼⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣶⣌⡛⢿⣽⢘⣿⣷⣿⡻⠏⣛⣀    \r\n     ⣼⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣦⠙⡅⣿⠚⣡⣴⣿⣿⣿⡆  \r\n   ⣰⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣷⠄⣱⣾⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿  \r\n ⢀⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⢸⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿  \r\n ⣸⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⡿⠣⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿  \r\n ⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⠿⠛  ⣿⣮⣝⣛⠿⠿⣿⣿⣿⣿  \r\n ⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣶        ⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⡟', 5),
