(42, 6, 'Peggle Deluxe is a perfect game. Not by itself necessarily, but it is one of the best \"background\" games. Watching a youtube video, talking with friends, talking with your therapist, zoom classes, on the phone while you\'re on hold. If you\'re a busy person and wanna turn off your brain, buy. this. game.', 5),
