(45, 6, 'Never got the chance to play this game back in the day but its still such a good game and it continues to hold up super well. Community can be pretty cringe at times with hackers and melvins but you can still have hella fun with your friends and online matches can still be really fun. Customizing your main is also super fun since all customization packs are fairly cheap.', 4),
(45, 10, 'Plants vs. Zombies GW2 is the deal of the decade, if you love FPS and are not the totally serious breed. The game is fun and addicting, a game that actually puts a smile on your face and makes you happy while you have fun. This could be the best 7.50 I ever spent on Steam. This game is Jam Packed with Havoc and Happiness, that is of course, if you like that kind of thing!', 4),
